item.title: CVE-2023-25588|2023-09-14T20:47:16.974Z -- fedora -- fedora%2037
item.description: A flaw was found in Binutils. The field `the_bfd` of `asymbol`struct is uninitialized in the `bfd_mach_o_get_synthetic_symtab` function, which may lead to an application crash and local denial of service.

item.title: CVE-2023-25585|2023-09-14T20:50:09.526Z -- fedora -- fedora%2037
item.description: A flaw was found in Binutils. The use of an uninitialized field in the struct module *module may lead to application crash and local denial of service.
